proposal.title: This is the BETA test of the Referendum Contract and the vote tallying mechanism. Please cast a vote, vote again with a different response, remove your vote, vote through a proxy, anything you can think of! Let's all help as a community to move the EOS mainnet into the spotlight as being the FIRST blockchain with on-chain governance accessible to all.
